name: Lady Greelanx
content: Lady Greelanx was the wife of Imperial Admiral Winstel Greelanx. She was disliked by the admiral, who had two mistresses. The two of them had two grown children, a son and a daughter and had a grandchild on the way in 4 BBY. She was widowed when Winstel died at the hands of Darth Vader.
